The paper focuses on program comprehension, which is a software engineering task, and proposes a novel neural network architecture for processing program source code. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, such as tree-based capsule networks, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper deals with programming languages and their syntactical structures, which is related to cs.PL (Programming Languages). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques to some extent, which is related to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
